soot.toDex

Class ConstantVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.AbstractConstantSwitch
      • soot.toDex.ConstantVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConstantSwitch, Switch

    public class ConstantVisitor
extends AbstractConstantSwitch
    A visitor that builds a list of instructions from the Jimple constants it visits.

    Use Switchable.apply(soot.util.Switch) with this visitor to add statements. These are added to the instructions in the StmtVisitor.
    Do not forget to use setDestination(Register) to set the storage location for the constant.
    See Also:
    StmtVisitor
